trans-unit.source: The DirectoryResponse class is the base class for request response classes, like the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse"></xref> and <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddResponse"></xref> classes.
trans-unit.target: DirectoryResponse 类是请求响应类的基类，如<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResponse"></xref>和<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.AddResponse"></xref>类。

trans-unit.source: The Controls property contains an array of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"></xref> objects returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: 控件属性包含的数组<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"></xref>服务器返回的对象。

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"></xref> objects returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: 数组<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl"></xref>服务器返回的对象。

trans-unit.source: The ErrorMessage property contains the error message, if any, for this operation.
trans-unit.target: 如果有的话，此操作，ErrorMessage 属性将包含错误消息。

trans-unit.source: The error message, if any, for this operation.
trans-unit.target: 错误消息中，如果有的话，此操作。

trans-unit.source: The MatchedDN property contains the matched distinguished name returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: MatchedDN 属性包含由服务器返回的匹配的可分辨的名称。

trans-unit.source: The matched distinguished name returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: 服务器返回的匹配可分辨的名称。

trans-unit.source: The Referral property contains the server referrals.
trans-unit.target: 引用属性包含服务器检索。

trans-unit.source: The RequestId property contains the Request Identifier.
trans-unit.target: RequestId 属性包含的请求的标识符。

trans-unit.source: User attempted to set the property value.
trans-unit.target: 用户试图进行设置的属性值。

trans-unit.source: The ResultCode property contains the result code of the operation.
trans-unit.target: ResultCode 属性包含该操作的结果代码。

trans-unit.source: The result code of the operation.
